{"data":[{"date":"22:00 03/08","title":"Sarri chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111i-\u1edf c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/sarri-chia-se-ve-tinh-hinh-dio-cua-cac-hoc-tro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, HLV Sarri th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois \u2013 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea, t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1ea1o ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u00d4ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111em v\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Jorginho, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn loay hoay v\u1edbi b\u00e0i to\u00e1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Sarri \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1o tin m\u1eebng cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V The Blues v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1ec1 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n mu\u1ed9n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Willian, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/HLV-Sarri-thua-nhan-khong-chac-tuong-lai-Courtois-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 Willian, nh\u01b0ng HLV Sarri th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi n\u00e9t m\u1eb7t lo \u00e2u h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. Sarri chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Courtois v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 CLB, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng Courtois s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Sarri th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Man City: &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. CLB mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u ngay t\u1ee9c kh\u1eafc. D\u00f9 v\u1eady v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Pep Guardiola l\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, hay \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Man City l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, b\u1edfi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh 2 n\u0103m, so v\u1edbi 2 tu\u1ea7n r\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-thua-nhan-la-fan-cung-cua-thuyen-truong-chelsea-172-193663.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/pep-thua-nhan-la-fan-cung-cua-thuyen-truong-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-thua-nhan-la-fan-cung-cua-thuyen-truong-chelsea-172-193663.html\">Pep th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 fan c\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u00f4n th\u1edd l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Pep ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 Sarri v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho HLV Chelsea nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city-172-193661.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city-172-193661.html\">3 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi d\u00e0nh cho Sarri tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap v\u1edbi Man City</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a The Blues d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ng\u1ed5n ngang nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1....</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1966","checkdouble":"193666"},{"date":"23:06 03/08","title":"Th\u1eafng Palestine, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn s\u1ee3 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestin-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y Park s\u1ee3 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 30, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Palestine. Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cS\u1edf d\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi e ng\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch do th\u00e1m. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u1eed 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn quay video. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng lo ng\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/thang-palestin-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Mr. Park c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay: \u201cCh\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi. \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng sai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. H\u00f4m nay, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a C\u0110V. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i duy tr\u00ec c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, b\u1edfi V-League \u0111ang b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n\u201d \u2013 HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, khi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n nhau 0-0. V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 5/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Oman v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 U23 Palestine</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ket-qua-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-tran-dau-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018-168-193660.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/ket-qua-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-tran-dau-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ket-qua-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-tran-dau-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018-168-193660.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u2013 TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1965","checkdouble":"193667"},{"date":"23:54 03/08","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mauricio Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao Spurs ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pochettino r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec Tottenham ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 20 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, duy nh\u1ea5t Tottenham l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 th\u00ec Spurs \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mauricio Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mauricio Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Mauricio-Pochettino-noi-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Pochettino ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Tottenham v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMauricio Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao Spurs ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Daniel \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n, t\u00f4i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Tottenham v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i HLV t\u00f4i c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi. Hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng BL\u0110 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Trong tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Tottenham s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh HLV Pochettino v\u1eabn h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, Tottenham kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 HLV Pochettino v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino tiep tuc co mot mua giai trang tay cung Tottenham\" title=\"Pochettino ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u1eafng tay c\u00f9ng Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/tottenham-chua-co-mot-tan-binh-nao-pochettino-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pochettino v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu Tottenham kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb trong m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ee3p. Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Oliver Skipp v\u00e0 Luke Amos, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang c\u00f3, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Tottenham \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSpurs v\u1eabn \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-tri-gia-30-trieu-bang-172-192555.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook c\u1ee7a Bournemouth</span>, Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a Manchester United v\u00e0 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1964","checkdouble":"193668"},{"date":"00:08 04/08","title":"Vi\u1ec7t Nam ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/10/22/hlv-hai-lo-toi-tu-tin-co-the-lam-tot-gdkt-o-doi-tuyen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n\u00d4ng H\u1ea3i &ldquo;l\u01a1&rdquo; khen ng\u1ee3i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 2-1. Sau tr\u1eadn, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua 7 ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t, v\u00ec v\u1eady chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n, phong c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Trong hi\u1ec7p 2 khi \u00f4ng Park \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u00f4m nay, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. C\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f2n v\u00e0i pha x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u00fang t\u00fang. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eeda.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u00d4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Palestine\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u1eebng ch\u00ea l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a HLV Miura c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/3/28/hlv-hai-lo-lai-khuyen-dt-viet-nam-da-bong-dai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00d4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Palestine</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i hay d\u00f9 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t. Pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u00ea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng ra bi\u00ean, r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ebf.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 ba \u0111\u00e0n anh b\u1ed5 sung cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng pha l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u00f2n pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t tinh t\u1ebf. V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ed9ng \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, c\u00f2n V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1eaft nh\u01b0 v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch, r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u00f4m nay, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&rdquo; &ndash; HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi-168-193668.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi-168-193668.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestin-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\">Th\u1eafng Palestine, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn s\u1ee3 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 U23 Palestine</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1963","checkdouble":"193669"},{"date":"00:24 04/08","title":"\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/de-gianh-chien-thang-mourinho-duoc-yeu-cau-lam-dieu-bat-ngo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, theo c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man United \u2013 Brian McClair.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMourinho ph\u1ea3i t\u01b0\u01a1i c\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00ec nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c nhau, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn M.U \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, khi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng trong tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 &ndash; Brian McClair kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eabn d\u1eaft M.U l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c th\u00fa v\u1ecb nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u00ec v\u1eady Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea1c quan h\u01a1n. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 n\u00f3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111ang th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec khi t\u1ecf ra nghi\u00eam t\u00fac, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng hay vui v\u1ebb. Sir Alex Ferguson c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u1eabn tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M.U, nh\u01b0ng t\u1eeb quan \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u00e1c C\u0110V s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng n\u1ebfu ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u00f4ng \u1ea5y m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t HLV r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan Jurgen Klopp, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u01a1i c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t vui v\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi b\u1ea1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man United, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&rdquo; &ndash; Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t, sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. N\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Bayern Munich, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng vui v\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-andreas-pereira-xung-dang-co-mat-trong-doi-hinh-mu-172-192629.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/quan-diem-andreas-pereira-xung-dang-co-mat-trong-doi-hinh-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-andreas-pereira-xung-dang-co-mat-trong-doi-hinh-mu-172-192629.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Sao tr\u1ebb gh\u00e9t b\u1ecb cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</span><br>\r\nAndreas Pereira x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19 v\u00e0 \u0111ang chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real: T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u01a1i &ldquo;c\u1eeda t\u1eed&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Man United s\u1ebd th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1962","checkdouble":"193670"},{"date":"05:46 04/08","title":"Tottenham ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o, Pochettino n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/tottenham-chua-co-mot-tan-binh-nao-pochettino-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mauricio Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao Spurs ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pochettino r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec Tottenham ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 20 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, duy nh\u1ea5t Tottenham l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 th\u00ec Spurs \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mauricio Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mauricio Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Mauricio-Pochettino-noi-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Pochettino ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Tottenham v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMauricio Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao Spurs ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Daniel \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n, t\u00f4i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Tottenham v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i HLV t\u00f4i c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi. Hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng BL\u0110 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Trong tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Tottenham s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh HLV Pochettino v\u1eabn h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, Tottenham kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 HLV Pochettino v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino tiep tuc co mot mua giai trang tay cung Tottenham\" title=\"Pochettino ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u1eafng tay c\u00f9ng Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/tottenham-chua-co-mot-tan-binh-nao-pochettino-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pochettino v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu Tottenham kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb trong m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ee3p. Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Oliver Skipp v\u00e0 Luke Amos, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang c\u00f3, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Tottenham \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSpurs v\u1eabn \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-tri-gia-30-trieu-bang-172-192555.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook c\u1ee7a Bournemouth</span>, Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a Manchester United v\u00e0 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1961","checkdouble":"193671"},{"date":"06:02 04/08","title":"\"Courtois s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/7/courtois-se-roi-chelsea-cap-ben-real-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Graeme Jones ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois, c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T B\u1ec9 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Graeme Jones d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Thibaut Courtois tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i. Hi\u1ec7n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-courtois-180-192010.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real quan t\u00e2m Courtois</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Graeme Jones ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Graeme Jones ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Graeme-Jones-phat-bieu-ve-Thibaut-Courtois-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Graeme Jones tin r\u1eb1ng&nbsp;</span>Courtois s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, h\u1ecd \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992. N\u1ebfu Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n&nbsp;Courtois \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng m\u1ed9t n\u0103m sau \u0111\u00f3. Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGraeme Jones ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois, c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T B\u1ec9 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Courtois ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Chelsea ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n b\u00e1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Real \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Courtois \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Real Madrid s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u1edbi Courtois&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Graeme Jones n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard v\u00e0 Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Real song The Blues \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n anh ra \u0111i. Alderweireld \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U quan t\u00e2m, song Spurs mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef anh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard va Real\" title=\"Hazard va Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-chuyen-huong-sang-Salah-va-Kane-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Graeme Jones c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai&nbsp;</span>Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld, c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T B\u1ec9 Graeme Jones ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;V\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Hazard, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Chelsea ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Hazard gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Alderweireld mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng Tottenham mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1960","checkdouble":"193672"},{"date":"06:34 04/08","title":"HLV Sarri ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/hlv-sarri-tiet-lo-so-tan-binh-con-lai-cap-ben-chelsea-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh, h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robert Green theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. 2 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/HLV-Maurizio-Sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/quan-chuc-chelsea-bay-toi-italia-chot-vu-rugani-172-192143.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea quan t\u00e2m trung v\u1ec7 Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus</span>, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Chelsea c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Chelsea c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea trong 10 n\u0103m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Maurizio Sarri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, song \u00f4ng \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi The Blues c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London trong 10 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri khong the tai hop voi Higuain o Chelsea\" title=\"HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Higuain \u1edf Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/juve-mua-bonucci-milan-muon-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c BL\u0110 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00ecnh trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y 10 n\u0103m, nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, ng\u00e0y mai t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n so v\u1edbi ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i l\u00e2u d\u00e0i \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng \u1edf Anh r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam t\u00fac \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)\u00a0\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1959","checkdouble":"193673"},{"date":"06:53 04/08","title":"V\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Joe Hart?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/19/voi-chi-4-trieu-bang-doi-bong-o-ngoai-hang-anh-da-co-joe-hart.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Joe Hart t\u1edbi Burnley l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ef1c cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Turf Moor.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Joe Hart s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Burnley</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u1edf Man City, \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Bravo. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile v\u00e0 Willy Caballero bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Torino theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart t\u1edbi Burnley v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Joe Hart t\u1edbi Burnley v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/Joe-Hart-toi-Burnley-voi-gia-4-trieu-bang-tu-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Joe Hart s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Burnley</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Willy Caballero ra \u0111i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Ederson, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u1ee7ng nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Joe Hart g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn West Ham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Hart ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, b\u1edfi v\u1eady West Ham quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng Man City, song v\u1edbi 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Pep kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u00e1n Joe Hart n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t thay v\u00ec cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Hart \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJoe Hart t\u1edbi Burnley l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ef1c cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Turf Moor v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Burnley.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Aberdeen v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Sean Dyche \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 ba \u1edf Europa League. Burnley nh\u1eafm Joe Hart b\u1edfi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, Nick Pope v\u00e0 Tom Heaton d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pep n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Joe Hart</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eddi Man City \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart t\u1edbi Burnley v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Joe Hart t\u1edbi Burnley v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/Joe-Hart-toi-Burnley-voi-gia-4-trieu-bang-tu-Man-City-hinh-anh-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Joe Hart ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xem \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp theo, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Joe Hart trong m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, n\u1ebfu ra \u0111i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho h\u1ecd t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd, t\u00f4i l\u00e0m v\u1eady v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ecdi CLB m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Joe Hart kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man City 2 n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, n\u1ebfu anh ra \u0111i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man City c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)\u00a0\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1958","checkdouble":"193674"},{"date":"05:32 04/08","title":"Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Vidal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Paulinho \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Arturo Vidal t\u1eeb Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mua thanh cong Vidal\" title=\"Barca mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-nham-arturo-vidal-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-192580.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mua Arturo Vidal</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 20 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;FC Barcelona v\u00e0 FC Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arturo Vidal, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. FC Barcelona s\u1ebd s\u1edbm th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Vidal, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVidal \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter v\u00e0 AC \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile, song Barca \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arturo Vidal n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi r\u1eddi Bayern?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Arturo Vidal c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia tay Bayern Munich, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n BL\u0110 v\u00e0 NHM \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vidal xac nhan roi Bayern toi Barca\" title=\"Vidal x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Bayern t\u1edbi Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/vidal-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vidal x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Bayern t\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00e1m \u01a1n BL\u0110 Bayern v\u00e0 NHM \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t th\u00edch th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Bayern Munich. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c \u1edf Barcelona, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Bayern&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i t\u00f4i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArturo Vidal tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, sau ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Malcom v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1957","checkdouble":"193675"},{"date":"15:04 03/08","title":"Liverpool gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/9/liverpool-giam-gia-ban-origi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool b\u00e1n Divock Origi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Origi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. \u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong ngo\u00e0i Roberto Firmino l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Sturridge, Danny Ings v\u00e0 Solanke, b\u1edfi v\u1eady r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Divock Origi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Divock Origi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Divock Origi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/9/liverpool-giam-gia-ban-origi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Origi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 t\u1ecf ra ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Wolfsburg theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 6 b\u00e0n sau 31 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Bundesliga.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nOrigi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool, anh v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Liverpool, Origi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng ra \u0111i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Origi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool b\u00e1n Divock Origi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"origi\" title=\"origi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/11/30/origi-toi-khong-nghi-liverpool-lai-thua-theo-cach-nhu-vay.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Origi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00f2i 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, song kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 cao. Theo The Mirror, Liverpool v\u1eeba gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Origi xu\u1ed1ng 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd nhanh ch\u00f3ng thanh l\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Hi\u1ec7n Watford \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Watford ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00f3 2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995. Ngo\u00e0i Watford th\u00ec Besiktas v\u00e0 Fenerbahce c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1956","checkdouble":"193640"},{"date":"15:21 03/08","title":"Toby Alderweireld l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/toby-alderweireld-len-tieng-ve-tin-don-chuyen-toi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Toby Alderweireld ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alderweireld l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c M.U quan t\u00e2m trung v\u1ec7 Toby Alderweireld. Mourinho \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Toby Alderweireld\" title=\"trung ve Toby Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/toby-alderweireld-len-tieng-ve-tin-don-chuyen-toi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Toby Alderweireld \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham, anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Jan Vertonghen v\u00e0 Davinson Sanchez. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 M.U chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989. M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, song v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Toby Alderweireld, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Tottenham \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00ednh m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Alderweireld l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Toby Alderweireld ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Toby Alderweireld\" title=\"Chelsea mua Toby Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/mu-muon-mua-alderweireld-mua-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Toby Alderweireld kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Tottenham, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Tottenham. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i h\u00e3y h\u1ecfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 Tottenham, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alderweireld, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-mua-yerry-mina-172-192619.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U s\u1ebd mua Yerry Mina </span>c\u1ee7a Barca ho\u1eb7c Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester. Theo Daily Mail v\u00e0 ESPN, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mina, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1955","checkdouble":"193641"},{"date":"15:02 03/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u0169 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Palestine?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-se-trung-thanh-voi-chien-thuat-cu-o-tran-viet-nam-vs-palestine.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 h\u00f4m nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>B\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam lu\u00f4n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u trong th\u1eddi gian qua, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup n\u0103m 2008 hay g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng quang c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i U15 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110N\u00c1 2017 ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Olympic-Viet-Nam-du-giai-tu-hung-quoc-te-Bai-test-quan-trong-cho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Vi\u1ec7c tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 7 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 Quang H\u1ea3i, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng hay Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh trung \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho nh\u1eefng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang sang Indonesia 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tranh \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a ai ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111i ASIAD b\u1edfi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. &ldquo;T\u00ednh c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t cao b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao. Ch\u01b0a ai l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111i d\u1ef1 Asiad c\u1ea3&rdquo;, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng &lsquo;h\u00edp&rsquo; n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u00f3 n\u00e9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23+3 trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Palestine, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 &ldquo;ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38-372-193643.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38-372-193643.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y 3/8 (Gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 cho nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o&nbsp;bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang kh\u00e1t m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng hay nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, ch\u00ednh Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m thay nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n cho c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh khi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y b\u1ecb theo k\u00e8m kh\u00e1 r\u00e1t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng thay v\u00ec ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3,&nbsp;gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League nh\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfn Linh, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c,&hellip; th\u1ea7y Park ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/olympicvn230-7-18-1532942727426829334077.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i. Ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 th\u00f4ng minh, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1997 n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u1eabn Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp, gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng ch\u1eafc, l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4n ngoan v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n xoay x\u1edf t\u1ed1t trong ph\u1ea1m vi h\u1eb9p, \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft hay ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao Ti\u1ebfn Linh, ngay c\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hay V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n sau khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U23 Palestine v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i nay 3/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y m\u00f9ng 5 v\u00e0 7/8. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd tr\u1ea3 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 m\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ra 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u01b0u t\u00fa nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo m\u00e0 c\u00f2n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i test c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a &lsquo;nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0ng&rsquo; &ndash; c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ecdi vui cho c\u00e1c \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-cho-man-tai-xuat-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-chau-a-168-193636.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/23/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-cho-man-tai-xuat-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-chau-a.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-cho-man-tai-xuat-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-chau-a-168-193636.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine: Ch\u1edd m\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam-168-193638.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam-168-193638.html\">Nh\u00f3m d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1eadp ri\u00eang, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u00e0o tay V\u0103n L\u00e2m</span><br>\r\nS\u00e1ng 3/8, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp ri\u00eang, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong-472-192622.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong-472-192622.html\">Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i khi th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto-Regular, serif; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1954","checkdouble":"193642"},{"date":"15:13 03/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y 3/8 (Gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Palestine gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 3/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 VI\u1ec6T NAM VS U23 PALESTINE</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oB6LYECsdcU\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> \u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, VFF ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Vinaphone \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, quy t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eed l\u1eeda v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c trong m\u1eaft HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n n\u1eeda n\u0103m, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn NHM r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p U23 Palestine. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 38 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 38 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/U23-Viet-Nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 100% quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1eb1m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng NHM, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea9n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho ASIAD v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 AFF Cup v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Do \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 nghi\u1ec7m n\u00ean c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01a1n tru khi th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ea1i g\u00ec bung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD. Thay v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1 &lsquo;ch\u1ebft b\u1ecf&rsquo; \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0103n \u00fd, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u1ea1c quan nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1eb7p U23 Palestine, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y trong n\u0103m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1 trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Palestine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t, gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: V\u0103n L\u00e2m; V\u0103n Thanh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\nU23 Palestine: Fahkouri; Alashhab, Farawi, Qatmish, Termanini, Abuwada, Fannoun, El-Kayed, Dabbagh, Yousef, Qymbor.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1953","checkdouble":"193643"},{"date":"17:29 03/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Man City gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Jesus v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/chinh-thuc-man-city-giu-chan-jesus-voi-hop-dong-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Man City.</h2><h2>Man City trao cho Jesus h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man City t\u1eeb Palmeiras v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2017, Gabriel Jesus \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 24 b\u00e0n sau 53 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Jesus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City trao h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2023. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean 40%, ch\u1ea1m m\u1ee9c 112.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Man City gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Jesus v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Man City gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Jesus v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/chinh-thuc-man-city-giu-chan-jesus-voi-hop-dong-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Jesus gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c C\u0110V v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u00f4i th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Man City l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi. B\u1edfi v\u00ec khi \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n c\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00f4i m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Man City c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c C\u0110V h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Man City khen ng\u1ee3i Jesus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Txiki Begiristain c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi khi The Citizens gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Jesus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJesus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. V\u1eady n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Pep Guardiola sung s\u01b0\u1edbng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Jesus th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1952","checkdouble":"193650"}]}